{"tid":1496173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［投票］幾號入機場錫春袋好？","createTime":"2019-08-22T11:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T05:38:24.000Z","uid":22607,"like":117,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9153b06687dcd2001236a35f28c01535199a2b","tid":1496173,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:34:54.000Z","msg":"琴晚開左個post傾入機場行動<br />\n<br />\n幾時先肯齊心入機場？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1494356\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1494356</a><br />\n<br />\n大家都好踴躍討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點黎喇！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我綜合左咁多位手足意見，得出左普遍同意嘅幾點：<br />\n1）要搵個冇同任何遊行撞期嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">星期六/星期日</span>，專注機場<br />\n2）要<span style=\"color: red;\">提早文宣</span><br />\n3）<span style=\"color: red;\">人數一定要夠多！！！！！</span>要做到812咁，好多人同時入機場，從而做到癱瘓陸路機場交通<br />\n<br />\n係日期上，好多手足都有提及1/9或者7/9，因為好似暫時未有活動？<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1/9嘅好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n日子近，冇咁多時間比港共準備，而且緊接嘅2/9係罷課，為罷課打響頭炮。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1/9嘅壞處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n緊接住31/8遊行，大家可能會累了，人數可能不足？而且有巴打提出星期日好似貨運量冇咁大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>7/9嘅好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n暫時完全未撞期，可以全日專注機場。星期六貨運量大，春袋之最。我地亦都有充足時間做文宣號召。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>7/9嘅壞處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n日期稍遠，港共可以慢慢諗對策對付我地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">綜合以上，大家不如投個靚票，決定想邊日錫春袋！<br />\n<br />\n9月1就正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月7就負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有其他日子/意見請手足踴躍提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3da894acb8bf1c8d123cd1425e0328c742a0b6a","tid":1496173,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f5d2ccaec4bdc8450af46a73bfd37d580731265","tid":1496173,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:36:03.000Z","msg":"今日中午個個沉了，同埋打錯野，所以重開"},{"pid":"57745708f59031fb77cd52e18ecee2c19c94ba10","tid":1496173,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:36:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4471dd9ae72ed835670ac20e8407c38341fb91b","tid":1496173,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"行動post冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e6e09e937dab7183b872f2bdda2f573e700728","tid":1496173,"uid":39864,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:37:24.000Z","msg":"824 0700 已經會入"},{"pid":"3f33178185a83850dc1fc996800b0021f635a556","tid":1496173,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:37:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0015c6d8d3973dca669e17c02978bc1413ecc8f4","tid":1496173,"uid":26090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"cb150066e185606c9b34b65b5f8bd7095b676c62","tid":1496173,"uid":22607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"07e6e09e937dab7183b872f2bdda2f573e700728","tid":1496173,"uid":39864,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:37:24.000Z","msg":"824 0700 已經會入"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:38:04.000Z","msg":"824個個撞左觀塘 未必會齊人<br />\n同埋機場一定要長搞"},{"pid":"76324e8d1fc961b68987d875708b9439d55fce91","tid":1496173,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:38:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df45f154250bf890a1fd4c173a75c33489333bdd","tid":1496173,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:38:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3433575271db18c8f39512